snippet.title: No Man's Sky - The Path Finder Update
snippet.description: The Path Finder Update introduces PS4 Pro support, planetary vehicles, base sharing, permadeath mode, ship specialisations and much more! Visit http://www.no-mans-sky.com/pathfinder-update/ for full details.
